      "name": "Pump pressure-rise validation against PIV and bench data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pressure rise across all 5 flow-speed operating points was compared against FDA-published experimental measurements. Mean absolute error was 4.2% across operating points, within the 10% acceptance criterion. Velocity field comparisons against PIV data showed good qualitative and quantitative agreement (R² = 0.94). The mesh independence study (activity: mesh-independence-study) is cited in the narrative as underpinning confidence in the discretization scheme, but the formal evidence record for that activity was captured separately in the project repository and was not linked here.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/cfd-pressure-validation-runs",
